## VM.tcpRedirections property

Contains an array of TCP port redirections that are usable. Especially, all ports specified in [VMConfig.redirectTCPPorts](./vm-providers.vmconfig.redirecttcpports.md) when calling the virtual machine factory should have a corresponding entry in this array.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
readonly tcpRedirections: readonly PortRedirection[];
```
